dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Madison_City_Zoning_2016.gdb. [City of Madison Wisconsin Zoning Districts http://www.cityofmadison.com/dpced/]
